    title: 'How Much Concrete Do I Need? Free Calculator & Guide For Tanzania',
    description: 'Learn how to calculate the exact amount of concrete you need for your project. Includes the formula, example calculations for slabs, foundations and columns, and tips for ordering ready mix concrete in Tanzania.',
    h1: 'How Much Concrete Do I Need? Volume Calculator & Guide',
    category: 'ready-mix-concrete-academy',
